summary: GUYS I’VE BEEN READING THIS REALLY GREAT FANFICTION AND I’D THOUGHT I’D SHARE IT!! IF YOU LIKE SHERLOCK AND MARVEL THEN THIS IS...
caption:
GUYS I’VE BEEN READING THIS REALLY GREAT FANFICTION AND I’D THOUGHT I’D SHARE IT!! IF YOU LIKE SHERLOCK AND MARVEL THEN THIS IS FOR YOU! ITS ONE OF MY FAVORITES SO FAR AND I REALLY LIKE THE AUTHOR, HER STUFF IS REALLY WELL WRITTEN!

Moving to England wasn't something Persephone was excited about, not that she was given a choice in the matter. But its not so bad when she’s introduced t a boy a little older than herself. He’s tall, svelte with curly hair.Everything about their relationship seems perfect in the beginning. Until monsters from her fathers past come to claim her as their own. And when she’s found, she.s different. 

She’s like Shattered glass…

summary: What if Thor used Stormbreaker to chop wood
body:
What if Thor used Stormbreaker to chop wood

Random thought but I had this idea occur to me like:

What if the avengers went on a camping trip and needed to chop firewood but there’s like no axe, then someone suggested Thor could use Stormbreaker instead.

But when he chops the wood, lightning strikes and everything explodes then Thor would be just pretending that it was an accident and someone would point out that lightning didn’t explode on Thanos when he hit him, and he would be like “it was a fluke” with an innocent face and all that.

Idk man but just a random thought
